   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>In the 4th year of our lord Probus Augustus, on Pauni 7, has paid Ptolemaios son of Iulianus, of the village of Karanis, 88 drachmai (for) the monthly anabolikon. I, Apolias, son of Aurelius Isidoros, have signed.</ab>
